OL,3,CCould 'stalking horse' Catherine West
OL,4,Cbring down Keir Starmer's leadership?
OL,6,FLabour MP Catherine West tells me she
OL,7,Fwill put herself up as a "stalking
OL,8,Fhorse" candidate on Monday morning,
OL,9,Feven though supporters of Andy Burnham
OL,10,Fhave asked her to hold off.
OL,12,FShe fears there is no certainty that
OL,13,Fthe Manchester mayor will get a seat
OL,14,Fin parliament and says the "current
OL,15,Fsituation has to be addressed with
OL,16,Furgency".
OL,18,FThe "radical change" needed by the
OL,19,Fgovernment cannot be delayed, she told
OL,20,Fme.
