OL,3,CCould 'stalking horse' Catherine West
OL,4,Cbring down Keir Starmer's leadership?
OL,6,FShe says she is nervous but has been
OL,7,Finundated with messages of support
OL,8,Ffrom fellow MPs.
OL,10,FAll that could stop her from launching
OL,11,Fher bid to unseat Starmer would be if
OL,12,Fthe Cabinet were to pre-empt her by
OL,13,Fforcing Starmer out. My cabinet
OL,14,Fsources tell me that looks unlikely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
